Package org.richfaces.cdi.push

Class Summary
PushCDIDependencyRegistrationExtension Registers all necessary beans required by PushCDIExtension extension.
PushCDIExtension CDI Extension for observing CDI events and delegating events with their payload to Push message bus.
TopicKeyResolver Bean for resolving TopicKey from Push annotation properties.
